1.0.name: connect20/Mage_CECA
1.0.description:
This is the payment module for the spanish payment gateway CECA-TPV. 
The Spanish Confederation of Savings Banks (CECA) is the National Association of 45 Spanish savings banks.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
